text: Sabratha University ( "Jamaa't Subrata") is one of Libya's largest public universities. It was established in 2015 in the city of Sabratha, Libya"Sabratha University" About with 18 campuses spread throughout cities on the coast west of the capital Tripoli. ==References== * Category:Universities in Libya Category:2015 establishments in Libya Category:Educational institutions established in 2015
